108
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,780
Sorry.

109
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,240
Sorry.

110
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,150
I'm fine.

111
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:10,190
I'm fine.

112
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:11,800
I can do it.

113
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,800
Good evening, Mr. Ji.

114
00:09:17,050 --> 00:09:19,360
