130
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:58,990
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

131
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,760
I don't want to miss it again.

132
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,440
Because I like you.

