♪ Walking through this world ♪

137
00:10:17,730 --> 00:10:21,730
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

138
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:21,350
Thank you for your hard work, everyone.

139
00:10:21,350 --> 00:10:23,210
The art exhibition was a complete success.

140
00:10:23,210 --> 00:10:25,760
It's a great start for Q3.

141
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,080
However,

142
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:29,880
regarding the safety incident
that occurred during the exhibition,

143
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:31,390
we will absolutely not compromise.

144
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:33,030
It must be dealt with seriously.

145
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:35,690
Now I will announce
the disciplinary decision.

146
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,800
Qian Xun, former director
of the sales department,

147
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,980
during the art exhibition,

148
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:46,400
was found to have committed
serious disciplinary violations.

149
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:47,510
[Purong Hotel]

150
00:10:46,530 --> 00:10:47,320
The circumstances are serious

151
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,180
and have caused adverse effects.

152
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:51,080
In accordance with the Purong Hotel

153
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,080
employee management regulations,

154
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,240
he has been dismissed.

155
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,510
Huang Chengmin, former director
of the finance department,

156
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:23,390
is suspected of conspiring

157
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,850
in Qian Xun's misconduct.

158
00:11:25,510 --> 00:11:28,240
The hotel's executive office
has unanimously decided

159
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:31,240
to terminate Huang Chengmin's
employment contract.

160
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:37,000
The above penalties take effect

161
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,510
from the date of this announcement.

162
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:41,110
I hope other departments
take this as a warning

163
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,980
and don't cause any more trouble.

164
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:44,790
Liu Zidong.

165
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:47,600
You will act as the Finance Director

166
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,270
and take over Huang Chengmin's work.

167
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:49,870
Yes.

168
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,960
As for the new Sales Director,

169
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,270
I will make the decision

170
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:04,840
after discussing it
with the HR Department.

171
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,150
Mr. Wei.

172
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:43,870
Aunt.

173
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,390
How long are you going to let Ji Feng

174
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:47,270
continue to make waves?

175
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:49,510
Feng Kaixin, Qian Xun,

176
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,640
and Huang Chengmin.

177
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:51,720
Before he came,

178
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,120
they were all the pillars

179
00:12:53,290 --> 00:12:54,870
and heroes of the hotel.

180
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:55,960
And now?

181
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:58,120
He drove them all away.

182
00:12:59,390 --> 00:13:00,600
His actions

183
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,590
are clearly targeting me.

184
00:13:02,610 --> 00:13:03,120
No,

185
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,000
he is also targeting you.

186
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,270
I know exactly

187
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:12,140
who's targeting me and who's trying to

188
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:15,480
hollow out Purong Hotel.

189
00:13:17,430 --> 00:13:18,550
Aunt,

190
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,960
don't be fooled by him.

191
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:22,980
I'm the one who hired him.

192
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:25,080
But you,

193
00:13:25,430 --> 00:13:27,750
I understand you less and less.

194
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:32,110
Fine.

195
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:33,750
I admit I'm stupid

196
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,350
and have no business talent.

197
00:13:35,470 --> 00:13:36,150
But what about Ji Feng?

198
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,550
What's so good about him?

199
00:13:37,930 --> 00:13:39,140
He's dictatorial,

200
00:13:39,170 --> 00:13:39,910
arrogant,

201
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:41,240
and dislikes everyone.

202
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:43,120
He fired 2 of my best men at once.

203
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:43,790
Aunt.

204
00:13:44,350 --> 00:13:45,000
If he wants to frame someone,

205
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,290
he can always find an excuse.

206
00:13:46,290 --> 00:13:48,870
The charges he made up
are completely baseless.

207
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:50,080
I think

208
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:52,230
an outsider of unknown origin like him

209
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,440
is the real threat to the hotel.

210
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:56,510
Siyuan.

211
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:58,600
Why is your thinking

212
00:13:58,660 --> 00:14:00,470
more old-fashioned than mine?

213
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:02,830
Our Purong Hotel

214
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:06,240
has never been
a complacent small workshop.

215
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:07,880
Embracing the new

216
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:09,330
is the important quality
of our Purong Hotel

217
00:14:09,330 --> 00:14:12,520
that allows us to gain
a foothold in Shanghai.

218
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,870
You're so territorial

219
00:14:15,350 --> 00:14:16,870
and old-fashioned.

220
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,740
If I leave Purong Hotel to you,

221
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:20,670
will it be okay?

222
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:33,020
Aunt.

223
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,130
I understand now.

224
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,920
From the very beginning,

225
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:40,010
you had it all figured out.

226
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:42,780
You just wanted to kick me aside, right?

227
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:45,360
Siyuan,

228
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:47,850
everything has a cause and effect.

229
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:51,360
I personally handed
the Purong Hotel over to you.

230
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,490
But you disappointed me.

231
00:14:54,010 --> 00:14:55,810
Then why did you only tell me now?

232
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,840
Why did you only tell me now,

233
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,440
Aunt?

234
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,440
I've spent almost half my life

235
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,510
at the Purong Hotel.

236
00:15:02,690 --> 00:15:05,800
Even if I haven't made any contributions,
I've worked hard.

237
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:06,920
Aunt,

238
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:08,840
at a time like this,

239
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,370
why are you telling me this?

240
00:15:10,850 --> 00:15:11,980
Why?

241
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,200
You should

242
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,720
ask yourself about this.

243
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,730
The person who let you down

244
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,440
is yourself.

245
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:30,510
Aunt.

246
00:15:32,050 --> 00:15:33,450
Your criticism is right.

247
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,630
I have disappointed you.

248
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:38,600
I'll go back

249
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:40,870
and think it over carefully.

250
00:15:41,110 --> 00:15:41,820
I'm sorry.

251
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:43,420
Please don't be angry.

252
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,120
I'll leave now.

253
00:15:56,090 --> 00:15:56,720
Ms. Wei,

254
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:58,280
should we notify the board?

255
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:01,200
No need.

256
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:03,190
We are family after all.

257
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:05,470
A scolding is enough.

258
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,530
I hope he behaves himself

259
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:10,760
and doesn't cause me any more trouble.

260
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:20,400
Miyu.

261
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:20,990
Mr. Ji.

262
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:26,460
Come.

263
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:28,440
Sit.

264
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:36,590
What's wrong?

265
00:16:37,610 --> 00:16:39,080
New Zealand Yuntian Group

266
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,630
is coming to Shanghai
for a bidding meeting project.

267
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:42,060
I want to give it another try.

268
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:42,910
How?

269
00:16:42,940 --> 00:16:45,010
I want to go directly
to their New Zealand headquarters

270
00:16:45,010 --> 00:16:47,040
to meet the director of
the International Marketing Department,

271
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:47,990
Eric Liang,

272
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:50,000
and try to bring the bidding meeting

273
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,440
directly to Purong.

274
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,640
This case is key to the performance VAM.

275
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:57,040
What reason do you have to convince me?

276
00:16:57,040 --> 00:16:58,470
I'm already familiar with all of

277
00:16:58,470 --> 00:17:00,000
their historical choices.

278
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:00,870
If I can't get it,

279
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:03,200
I'm willing to take full responsibility.

280
00:17:06,510 --> 00:17:07,069
Okay.

281
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:09,069
Let me think about it.

282
00:17:09,710 --> 00:17:11,170
I'll wait to hear from you.

283
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,550
About Miyu's application
to go to New Zealand,

284
00:17:25,550 --> 00:17:27,079
are you going to approve it?

285
00:17:27,859 --> 00:17:29,120
I'm thinking about it.

286
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:30,640
Do you know how many
percentage points we are away

287
