574
00:30:57,050 --> 00:30:59,180
The baby's only just past 100 days old,

575
00:30:59,330 --> 00:31:01,460
and already looks so much like his dad.

576
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:03,830
This high forehead,

577
00:31:03,850 --> 00:31:05,320
chubby nose,

578
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:07,350
and these big, dark,

579
00:31:07,370 --> 00:31:08,700
bright eyes.

580
00:31:13,070 --> 00:31:13,930
Zhenzhen.

581
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:15,160
I just remembered

582
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,050
I have an urgent matter to attend to.

583
00:31:16,050 --> 00:31:17,750
I really have to go now.

584
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:19,510
If anything comes up later,

585
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:20,510
just contact Secretary Wu directly.

586
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,510
It's the same.

587
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:22,440
Okay.

588
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:25,780
Then I'll come by your house
for a visit another day.

589
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:33,150
What are you visiting for?

590
00:31:33,150 --> 00:31:34,610
Who are you going to visit?

591
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,510
You just carry a baby

592
00:31:35,510 --> 00:31:37,000
to extort me, right?

593
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:40,700
Don't wake the baby.

594
00:31:45,030 --> 00:31:45,590
Mr. Wei.

595
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:47,550
I thought I was being too subtle

596
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:49,080
and you didn't understand.

597
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,510
The report makes it very clear

598
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:53,240
whether the child is yours.

599
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:57,780
[DNA Paternity Test Report]

600
00:31:57,810 --> 00:31:58,800
[for Nie Quan and Wei Siyuan]

601
00:31:58,820 --> 00:32:00,060
[Paternal probability: 99.999%]

602
00:32:02,290 --> 00:32:04,530
[Conclusion]

603
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,640
Didn't I tell you

604
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,000
to get an abortion?

605
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:13,330
I'm his mother.

606
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:15,180
Whether to keep it or not is my choice.

607
00:32:15,180 --> 00:32:17,490
Then what do you want from me now?

608
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:18,410
Calm down.

609
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,920
I'm not forcing you to acknowledge him.

610
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,450
I just want you to do me a favor

611
00:32:21,450 --> 00:32:23,110
so I can raise him alone

612
00:32:23,110 --> 00:32:24,590
and give him a better life.

613
00:32:24,990 --> 00:32:26,320
What if I don't help you?

614
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,270
Then I can't guarantee

615
00:32:28,290 --> 00:32:29,950
that your wife won't find out.

616
00:32:38,810 --> 00:32:39,910
Alright, tell me.

617
00:32:40,020 --> 00:32:41,140
How can I help you?

618
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:43,230
Make me the Sales Director.

619
00:32:44,810 --> 00:32:46,360
You have quite an appetite.

620
00:32:46,390 --> 00:32:47,680
You're already a Sales Manager.

621
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:49,760
Isn't the money you make
enough to raise a child?

622
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,460
Mr. Wei,

623
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:52,540
do I need to remind you

624
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:54,290
that if you don't promote me,

625
00:32:54,290 --> 00:32:56,180
Ji Feng will promote Xu Miyu?

626
00:32:56,430 --> 00:32:59,190
Your right-hand men have already
been taken out by him.

627
00:32:59,190 --> 00:33:00,250
If this continues,

628
00:33:00,530 --> 00:33:02,790
how much of a chance
do you think you have?

629
00:33:04,820 --> 00:33:05,860
Here's the case.

630
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:07,910
Ji Feng just went to my aunt

631
00:33:07,930 --> 00:33:09,770
and filed a serious complaint against me.

632
00:33:09,770 --> 00:33:10,700
The one in my family,

633
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:11,660
that tigress,

634
00:33:11,990 --> 00:33:13,180
is not to be trifled with.

635
00:33:13,180 --> 00:33:14,800
I can't afford to offend her either.

636
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:15,800
At this juncture,

637
00:33:15,830 --> 00:33:17,190
if I rashly promote you,

638
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,350
aren't you afraid my...

639
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:20,550
That depends on your own tricks.

640
00:33:20,900 --> 00:33:23,560
You've been running
the hotel for so many years.

641
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:25,050
To promote one of your own,

642
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,800
do you still need someone else's approval?

643
00:33:27,850 --> 00:33:28,840
Besides,

644
00:33:28,990 --> 00:33:32,110
I know exactly how you
and Director Qian have been

645
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:34,160
lining your pockets together.

646
00:33:34,330 --> 00:33:35,330
Promote me,

647
00:33:35,360 --> 00:33:36,480
and with my cooperation,

648
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,210
you'll only get more benefits.

649
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:39,130
What do you say?

650
00:33:44,850 --> 00:33:45,850
Please help

651
00:33:45,870 --> 00:33:47,550
your own flesh and blood.

652
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:13,860
Great.

653
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:16,659
Xu Miyu is getting more and more amazing.

654
00:34:16,770 --> 00:34:18,670
She made our hotel stand out
among so many competitors,

655
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:20,239
even beating Kuanli.

656
00:34:23,179 --> 00:34:24,570
Are you listening to me?

657
00:34:29,969 --> 00:34:30,969
I heard you.

658
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:33,400
You said Miyu is amazing.

659
00:34:35,570 --> 00:34:38,810
We got the bidding meeting
from Yuntian Group.

660
00:34:38,929 --> 00:34:40,659
Why do you look unhappy?

661
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,590
I'm not.

662
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:44,940
I'm your senior.

663
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:47,560
Do you think I can't tell
if you're happy or not?

664
00:34:51,030 --> 00:34:51,989
I am very happy.

665
00:34:54,060 --> 00:34:55,590
You don't look happy at all.

666
00:35:13,950 --> 00:35:14,590
Morning.

667
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:20,780
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

668
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:23,880
♪ Don't look back ♪

669
00:35:25,090 --> 00:35:26,910
♪ I've already learned ♪

670
00:35:27,490 --> 00:35:31,290
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

671
00:35:28,510 --> 00:35:30,230
Ms. Xu.

672
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:31,710
You are so amazing.

673
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:32,230
You have no idea

674
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:33,440
when I received
the email from Yuntian Group,

675
00:35:32,310 --> 00:35:33,800
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

676
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:35,010
how excited I am!

677
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:38,950
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

678
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:36,720
That wasn't just an email.

679
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:38,510
That's our team's annual bonus.

680
00:35:38,510 --> 00:35:39,360
Exactly.

681
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:40,440
I'm so happy.

682
00:35:39,690 --> 00:35:42,550
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

683
00:35:41,810 --> 00:35:43,920
After this bidding meeting is completed,

684
00:35:43,300 --> 00:35:45,750
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

685
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,110
let's have a good celebration.

686
00:35:45,110 --> 00:35:45,880
Okay?

687
00:35:46,030 --> 00:35:46,840
Okay, Ms. Xu.

688
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,970
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

689
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,520
Okay.

690
00:35:50,030 --> 00:35:50,880
Ms. Xu.

691
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:54,330
Mr. Ji asked you
to go to the meeting room.

692
00:35:54,520 --> 00:35:55,250
Okay.

693
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,270
Everyone.

694
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:41,020
We have just 1 month left

695
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,980
before the VAM agreement settlement date.

696
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:43,670
Ms. Xu

697
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:46,470
won us the Yuntian Group
bidding meeting project.

698
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:47,710
This is both our hope

699
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,230
and a test for us.

700
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:51,230
We must go all out.

701
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:53,230
Director Lu, Director Bai.

702
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:54,000
-Yes.
-Yes.

703
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,190
I'll give you three days.

704
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:56,440
The marketing department
and the Front Office

705
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:58,260
must both provide
their respective reception plans.

706
00:36:58,260 --> 00:36:58,960
Yes.

707
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:05,670
I will announce a personnel appointment

708
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:07,150
for the sales department.

709
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:14,040
This is Meng Jie, the new director
of the sales department.

710
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:15,630
She will be fully responsible for

711
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:18,230
the sales department's
future work meetings.

712
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:19,550
Hello, everyone.

713
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:21,630
I hope we can work well together.

714
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:22,360
Thank you.

715
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:24,510
Wasn't it supposed to be Ms. Xu?

716
00:37:24,510 --> 00:37:25,280
What happened?

717
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:26,540
This is so unexpected.

718
00:37:30,590 --> 00:37:31,700
Any objections?

719
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,140
Director Meng.

720
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,510
For this bidding meeting,

721
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:42,070
all sales department employees need to

722
00:37:42,070 --> 00:37:43,550
form groups and participate

723
00:37:43,550 --> 00:37:45,330
in customer development for each project.

724
00:37:45,330 --> 00:37:46,110
We will

725
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,480
use this opportunity to develop

726
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,640
our potential customers.

727
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:49,400
Okay.

728
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:52,110
But I need someone to assist me.

729
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,030
Ms. Xu.

730
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,920
You are most familiar with
the content of the bidding meeting.

731
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,730
For the time being,

732
00:37:57,730 --> 00:37:59,230
please cooperate more with Director Meng.

733
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:00,120
The specific details

734
00:38:00,120 --> 00:38:01,850
can be synchronized after the meeting.

735
00:38:01,850 --> 00:38:02,440
Okay.

736
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:07,370
Mr. Ji.

737
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:12,590
Why did you have a meeting

738
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:14,160
without calling me?

739
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,280
It's just some trivial matters.

740
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,630
I didn't dare to bother you, Mr. Wei.

741
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:18,630
What do you mean by bother?

742
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:19,630
That's a bit much.

743
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:22,280
I just heard that you recently

744
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:25,140
appointed a new director
for the sales department.

745
00:38:25,730 --> 00:38:27,880
I figured they are my future colleagues,

746
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:30,210
so I came over
specifically to take a look.

747
00:38:32,050 --> 00:38:33,180
By the way, Mr. Ji,

748
00:38:33,330 --> 00:38:35,540
I also have
a new personnel appointment here.

749
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:37,340
I'd like to ask for your opinion.

750
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,580
Please go ahead, Mr. Wei.

751
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:41,980
There's a manager in the sales department
named Lu Zhenzhen.

752
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:43,110
You know her, right?

753
00:38:46,860 --> 00:38:47,510
Of course.

754
00:38:47,510 --> 00:38:48,360
I completely trust

755
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:49,960
the newly appointed Director Meng

756
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,500
can lead the sales department well.

757
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:52,760
But after all, she just arrived.

758
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:54,480
She isn't familiar with many things yet,

759
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,630
and needs someone by her side

760
00:38:55,630 --> 00:38:57,440
to help out and coordinate.

761
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:58,510
I heard that

762
00:38:58,510 --> 00:38:59,540
Ms. Lu

763
00:38:59,560 --> 00:39:00,680
is very capable

764
00:39:00,710 --> 00:39:02,440
and was Purong's top sales rep.

765
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:03,550
Although

766
00:39:03,570 --> 00:39:05,250
she hasn't been here long either,

767
00:39:05,250 --> 00:39:07,620
the sales department
is in need of people right now.

768
00:39:07,620 --> 00:39:09,630
We should recruit talents
without overstressing qualifications.

769
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:10,400
So,

770
00:39:10,950 --> 00:39:12,130
I want to promote her to

771
00:39:12,130 --> 00:39:13,730
vice director of the sales department.

772
00:39:13,730 --> 00:39:14,580
Mr. Ji,

773
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:16,030
what do you think?

774
00:39:24,670 --> 00:39:25,360
Susan.

775
00:39:25,780 --> 00:39:27,690
Remember to handle this
for Mr. Wei after the meeting.

776
00:39:27,690 --> 00:39:28,770
Okay, Mr. Ji.

777
00:39:31,100 --> 00:39:31,790
Alright.

778
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:32,830
That's it.

779
00:39:33,710 --> 00:39:34,690
You guys continue.

780
00:39:34,690 --> 00:39:35,400
Okay.
